cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IT, cs.MS

This paper involves the use of shape matching and statistical models for multi-organ deformation reconstruction, which are common techniques in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI). The paper also discusses the use of kernel methods for deformation learning, which falls under information theory (cs.IT) and mathematical statistics (cs.MS).
